1. *Boja* se lako može promeniti. (The color can be easily changed.)
2. Boja ovog oblaka je crna. (The color of this cloud is black.)
3. *Bojama* se može istaći nešto. (Colors can be used to emphasize something.)
4. Boja očiju mu je plava. (His eyes are blue.)
5. Ova boja je veoma svetla. (This color is very bright.)
6. *Bojanje* noktiju je nešto što voli da radi. (Painting her nails is something she likes to do.)